Objectives
	- To develop a system that allocates inputs to the farmers during the issuing of inputs process to minimize bias and promote fairness, the 	 	  issuing will be based on the land the famer has to his possess and the inputs that are available 
	- To develop a system that calculates the cultivated land from the pictures obtain from a remote satellite
	- To develop a system that is able to monitor the land that has been cultivated against the inputs that has been given to farmer before the 		  season commenced, and notify for any fraud act on the inputs given to a farmer.  
